Poseur Female Noble: Gosh almighty! Didn't His Majesty King Theodore
take an oath, promising our safety?
Distressed Female Noble: What do we do now? Where's everybody headed?
Frightened Male Noble: Yikes, look ahead!
Poseur Female Noble: Oh mon dieu, HELP ME!
Angelia: Too dangerous here, everyone follow my lead!
Poseur Female Noble: Hmph! You single-handedly started this massacre!
Frightened Male Noble: Exactly, who trusts you anymore?!
Naya: The lady doth protest too much, methinks. Want to turn into monster mash? BE MY GUEST!
Naya: Those who want to die another day, stay close behind me!
Poseur Female Noble: ...Perhaps, we should find another place to stay...
Distressed Female Noble: That's right, so what are we waiting for? Let's go!
Angelia: It should be safe ahead, hurry up...
Naya: We're almost there. Don't you try to stop us!
Naya: Curses... my stamina has its limits...
Angelia: Must, leave, NOW...
Naya: Argh... how many of you are there!!!
Poseur Female Noble: Waaaahhh... Is this the end for us...
Frightened Male Noble: This forsaken place IS NOT to die for...
Angelia: As royalty, I will do that which is good, and ensure no harm shall comes to the people of the Sun!
Dylan: Don't you dare touch the princess!
Angelia: Colonel Levon!
Naya: Sione, my dearest!
Dylan: Your Highness, the Sunshine Infantry is at your service! Apologies for the late arrival!
Angelia: Not at all, how could I ever thank you!
Naya: Yes, better late than never, I'd say!
Angelia: Hush please. Now take these nobles elsewhere!
Theodore: ...SAFE? Traitor, think you'll pass judgement?
Angelia: Uncle...
